#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: apps/site/src/app/[locale]/terms/page.tsx:34
msgid "二、合理使用"
msgstr "2. Acceptable use"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: apps/site/src/app/[locale]/terms/page.tsx:37
msgid "请不要利用隐界从事违反所在国家或地区法律的活动；不要将其用于骚扰、欺诈、传播虚假信息或制造伤害。AI 角色生成的内容由用户负责审阅与判断，不视为隐界开发者的立场或建议。"
msgstr "Don't use Enclave for activities that break the laws of your jurisdiction. Don't use it for harassment, fraud, disinformation, or to harm others. AI-generated content is the user's responsibility to review — it is not an opinion or recommendation of the Enclave maintainers."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: apps/site/src/app/[locale]/terms/page.tsx:44
msgid "三、订阅与计费"
msgstr "3. Subscription & billing"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: apps/site/src/app/[locale]/terms/page.tsx:47
