msgstr "If you subscribe to our managed cloud, billing is tied to the model provider you connect and metered by usage. You can cancel anytime; unused portions are prorated monthly and refunded."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: apps/site/src/app/[locale]/terms/page.tsx:54
